<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="L" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Leer2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Leer,</orth> vb. to look smilingly, to simper, to smile: <cit><quote>you l. upon me,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.480" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL V, 2, 480</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I will l. upon him,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 5.5.7" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B V, 5, 7</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I will no more trust him when he --s,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 5.1.97" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. V, 1, 97</bibl></cit>.
